OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine. Remaining dry this
OL,7,Fafternoon with some good spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine and patchy cloud. Light and
OL,9,Fvariable winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry and
OL,12,Fclear with some patchy frost. Clouding
OL,13,Fover from the south in the early hours
OL,14,Fwith a few showers breaking out in the
OL,15,Fsouthwest.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FChance of some showery rain
OL,18,Fin the morning otherwise dry. Rather
OL,19,Fcloudy but some bright spells may
OL,20,Fbreak through at times. Very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
