OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fspreading east on Thursday afternoon,
OL,7,Fclearing the east early on Friday.
OL,8,FThen Friday and Saturday will be dry
OL,9,Fwith some brightness.
